@ontos 1.0
@title Obsidian example vault
@type team-knowledge

- Knowledge base @id(knowledge-base) #vault
  status: active
  purpose: Test local reading and preview behavior in Obsidian.
  verify:
    - Open the file in the example vault.
    - Run the preview command.

  - Reference node @id(reference-node) #link
    purpose: Confirm [[knowledge-base]] references are visible.
